<div id="review_2830533466" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2830533466" />
    <a title="Wendy Powell" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/60850444-wendy-powell"><img alt="Wendy Powell" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2830533466?book_show_action=true">May 22, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wendy Powell" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wendy Powell" href="/user/show/60850444-wendy-powell">Wendy Powell</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2830533466" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11391966677800773255">I chose this book as I am interested in the subject and whilst on holiday last year visited one of the work houses in the area of Ireland that this was set. My visit had a lasting effect and I wanted to find out more. The story didnt really tell me any more than I already knew and was very repetitive. It didnt really hold my interest and as a result I found I didnt really care about the characters because of the lack of emotive writing. I did manage to finish it but it was tough going.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


