<li class='cover' id='bookCover_31137530'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/31137530-the-great-famine"><img alt="The Great Famine: The History of the Irish Potato Famine during the Mid-19th Century" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1468742110l/31137530._SX98_.jpg" />
